"format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best rows for men are the front rows and the worst are the back rows. The best rows for women are the back rows and the worst are the front rows.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 440\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14165,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/13\/something-happens-in-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":26118,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: If something happens during the prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGlorification of Allah is for men and clapping is for women.\u201d Ibn al-Muthna added, \"If something happens in prayer.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1145, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 423 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28535,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/30\/salat-women-masjid-haram-nabawi\/","url_meta":{"origin":26118,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Best prayer for women at home, except sacred mosques","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Amr a